Package com.example.mborper.breathbetter.bluetooth

Class IBeaconFrame

java.lang.Object
com.example.mborper.breathbetter.bluetooth.IBeaconFrame
public class IBeaconFrame extends Object
The IBeaconFrame offers getters to obtain the data stored on the beacons the app scans. It's primarily used to obtain uuid, major and minor.
Author:
Jordi Bataller i Mascarell
